<hr />
<div class="image-container aligncenter"><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/4/49/Happy-afternoon-golden-retriever-yoko_%2824326853815%29.jpg" alt="Happy-afternoon-golden-retriever-yoko_%2824326853815%29.jpg" class="image" /></div>
<hr />
<p><strong>$250 Reward</strong><br />
Last spotted on September 16th near Hyde Park<br />
Very friendly and playful, loves to play chase<br />
Responds to &quot;Goldie&quot;<br /></p>
<hr />
<p><strong>If found, please call 306-555-4417</strong><br />
Please help us find our baby</p>
</div>
</blockquote>
</div>
